THE <br>RESORT

Jannata Resort & Spa is a boutique property with tranquil valley views in the rural village of Sebali, just outside of Ubud.<br><br>It is attuned to the surrounding environment through a thoughtful design that respects Bali’s rich artistry and cultural heritage.
READ THE STORY

THE STAY

<p>Stylish accommodation option at Jannata Resort &amp; Spa incorporates a choice of 2 Superior Rooms, 16 Deluxe Suites, 6 One Bedroom Pool Villas and 1 Two Bedroom Pool Villa to anticipate all of your holiday needs. All categories are the epitome of Balinese luxury with customized interiors and essential home comforts.</p>

DINE AT AMATERAS

<p>Amateras Restaurant at Jannata Resort &amp; Spa serves an extensive menu of Western and Asian cuisine that is driven by quality ingredients.</p><p><br></p><p>The restaurant is located next to the lobby and extends out onto an open terrace for an alfresco dining experience. It is elevated over the main swimming pool with tropical views of lush valley greenery in the distance.</p>

WELLNESS AT JANNATA

A sanctuary for the senses, Champaka Spa features a comfortable lounge area and three private treatment rooms for sessions of personal rejuvenation. This charming wellness facility overlooks a tropical valley that descends down to flowing river.
